{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Atomics.add()","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/add","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects\">Standard built-in objects</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics\"><code>Atomics</code></a></strong></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Métodos</strong></a><ol><li><em><code>Atomics.add()</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/and\"><code>Atomics.and()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/compareExchange\"><code>Atomics.compareExchange()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/exchange\"><code>Atomics.exchange()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/isLockFree\"><code>Atomics.isLockFree()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/load\"><code>Atomics.load()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/notify\"><code>Atomics.notify()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/or\"><code>Atomics.or()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/store\"><code>Atomics.store()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/sub\"><code>Atomics.sub()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/wait\"><code>Atomics.wait()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/waitAsync\"><code>Atomics.waitAsync()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/xor\"><code>Atomics.xor()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li><strong>Herança:</strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Propriedades</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Métodos</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>O método estátitico&nbsp;<code><strong>Atomics</strong></code><strong><code>.add()</code></strong> adiciona um dado valor em&nbsp;uma determinada posição no array e retorna o valor antigo daquela posição. Esta operação atômica garante que nenhuma outra escrita ocorra&nbsp;até que o valor modificado seja escrito de volta.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">Atomics.add(typedArray, index, value)\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parâmetros","title":"Parâmetros","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"typedarray\"><code>typedArray</code></dt>\n <dd>Um array tipado de inteiros compartilhado. Pode ser <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>Int8Array</code></a>, <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>Uint8Array</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Int16Array\"><code>Int16Array</code></a>, <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>Uint16Array</code></a>, <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>Int32Array</code></a>, ou&nbsp;<a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>Uint32Array</code></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"index\"><code>index</code></dt>\n <dd>A posição no&nbsp;<code>typedArray</code> onde o&nbsp;<code>value</code> será adicionado.</dd>\n <dt id=\"value\"><code>value</code></dt>\n <dd>Número que será adicionado.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valor_de_retorno","title":"Valor de retorno","isH3":true,"content":"<p>O valor antigo na determinada posição (<code>typedArray[index]</code>).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exceções","title":"Exceções","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Lança uma exceção&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypeError\"><code>TypeError</code></a>, se o&nbsp;<code>typedArray</code> não for um dos tipos de inteiro permitidos.</li>\n <li>Lança uma exceção <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypeError\"><code>TypeError</code></a>, se o&nbsp;<code>typedArray</code> não for tipo array tipado compartilhado.</li>\n <li>Lança uma exceção <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>RangeError</code></a>, se o&nbsp;<code>index</code> estiver fora dos limites no&nbsp;<code>typedArray</code>.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplos","title":"Exemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> sab <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">SharedArrayBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1024</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> ta <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Uint8Array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>sab<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nAtomics<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">add</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>ta<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">12</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// retorna 0, o valor antigo</span>\nAtomics<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">load</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>ta<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 12</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-atomics.add\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'Atomics.add' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>Definição inicial no ES2017.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Recurso</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span> [2]</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/55\" title=\"Released on 2017-08-08.\">55</a> (55) [1]</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Recurso</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>55.0 (55) [1]</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] No Firefox da versão&nbsp;46&nbsp;até a versão 54, este recurso fica desabilitado por uma configuração. Em about:config, altere o&nbsp;<code>javascript.options.shared_memory</code> para&nbsp;<code>true</code>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>[2] A implementação está sob desenvolvimento e necessita dessas flags de runtime: <code>--js-flags=--harmony-sharedarraybuffer --enable-blink-feature=SharedArrayBuffer</code></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics\"><code>Atomics</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/sub\"><code>Atomics.sub()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"sintaxe"},{"text":"Exemplos","id":"exemplos"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O método estátitico Atomics.add() adiciona um dado valor em uma determinada posição no array e retorna o valor antigo daquela posição. Esta operação atômica garante que nenhuma outra escrita ocorra até que o valor modificado seja escrito de volta.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Atomics.add()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Atomics.add()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Atomics.add()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Atomics.add()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Atomics.add()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Atomics.add()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/atomics/add","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/atomics/add/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"Referência JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/doc